{"article_id":"pzgoj8Sn60r9CTzb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Treasury Secretary Jack Lew says","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"there is n't much time .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"Congress and the White House face two big deadlines","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"to fund the government .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"It will be an intricate maneuver to meet both deadlines","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"even as congressional leadership changes .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"And in an interview with NPR , Lew described behind-the-scenes negotiations","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"meant to avert a last-minute crisis .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"`` There are conversations","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"going on at a staff level , ''","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Lew told NPR 's Steve Inskeep ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"`` and I think","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"the key is for Democrats and Republicans","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"[ in Congress ]","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"to talk to each other . ''","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"From his office at the Treasury Department , Lew commented on the challenge","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"of doing what should be the routine business of government .","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"A Congress","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"that was never designed","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"to act quickly ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"and that 's been made dysfunctional by partisanship ,","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"must resolve multiple problems within weeks .","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"House Speaker John Boehner retires at the end of October ;","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"Republicans are voting today on his successor .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"By Nov. 5 ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Lew says ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Congress must raise the federal debt limit","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"to allow the government to meet its obligations .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Then in December comes a deadline","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"to approve spending","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"and avert a government shutdown .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Lew insists","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"the administration will not negotiate over the debt limit .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"`` We have made it clear","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that we are not going to let the debt ceiling be used as a way","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"to extract commitments","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"that otherwise would be unacceptable . ''","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Yet Lew acknowledged","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"that there is a larger conversation underway about measures","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that could address both the borrowing and spending deadlines ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"and possibly pass","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"before Speaker Boehner steps down .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"Negotiators are trying to hammer out something substantive","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"to change the so-called sequester , a series of across-the-board defense and spending cuts","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"put in place in recent years .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"With Boehner exiting ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"there 's the potential for a longer-term budget deal , possibly two years ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"that could be passed with Democratic support .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Neither Boehner nor Republican Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell has shown any interest in another government shutdown over the debt limit .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Boehner has also promised to `` clean the barn ''","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"before he leaves .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Lew 's comments come","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"as House Republicans are set to vote","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"to pick their nominee","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"to be replace Boehner .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"White House officials say","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"there are open lines of communication","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"and point to `` shared goals . ''","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"Lew was also echoing some of what President Obama said at a press conference Friday .","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"`` When it comes to the debt ceiling ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"we 're not going back there , ''","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Obama said .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"But ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"the president added ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"`` I do think","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"there is still a path for us","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"to come up with a reasonable agreement","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"that raises the spending caps above sequester","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"to make sure","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"that we can properly finance both our defense and nondefense needs ,","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"that maintains a prudent control of our deficits ,","depth":15},{"id":71,"text":"and that we can do that in short order . ''","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"`` We 've always said","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"if it 's easier to combine it with something else","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"that 's mutually acceptable ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"that 's a form question , ''","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"Lew said ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"adding ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"`` that 's for Congress to decide .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"We 've told them","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"they need to raise the debt limit .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"If combining a couple of things together","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"that are on their way towards approval","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"makes it easier","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"- what they ca n't do is ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"it ca n't be used","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"to extract an unacceptable policy commitment . ''","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"The debt ceiling has been routinely raised in the past -","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"that is , until the 2010 wave election","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"that saw Republicans take over the U.S. House","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"fueled by an influx of Tea Party candidates .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"The Tea Party has made the national debt ,","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"which is now more than $ 18 trillion ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"a key part of its platform .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"In 2011 and 2013 , Tea Party members ' push","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"to cut spending","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"rather than raise the debt limit","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"pushed the country to the brink of default .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Negotiations on major spending reform in 2011 between Obama and Boehner failed ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"and then , in 2013 , the fight over the debt limit led to a partial government shutdown .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Treasury warned","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"that the country was within a day","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"of not being able to make its debt payments ,","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"to reopen the government ,","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Boehner resorted to relying on Democratic votes , an unusual maneuver for the majority .","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"There 's motivation from both sides this time around","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"in getting a deal done , in large measure , because the future appears so unpredictable .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"With Boehner gone ,","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"there 's no telling what the strategy will be of the new House Republican leadership team","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"that is not even in place yet .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"`` Getting to the day","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"before we ca n't pay our bills , the day","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"before the government of the United States might default for the first time in its history , ''","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"Lew told NPR ,","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"`` we should n't get even close to it .","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"So the notion","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"that the deadline is the last possible moment","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"to act","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"is a mistake .","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"And it 's a mistake","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"which Congress should avoid . ''","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"On what tools Treasury is trying to use","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"to help create jobs","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"and raise wages","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"`` We 're continuing to advocate doing something like combining business tax reform with infrastructure","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"to use the one-time revenue","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"that comes from business tax reform","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"to have a big increase in our infrastructure investment .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"So I think","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"some of the solutions are quite clear ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"if we could only get the political process to produce them . ''","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"`` What I announced was we were going to be putting out a whole new family of bills , not just the $ 10 bill ,","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"but we 're going to be redesigning the other bills in this new series .","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"And I said","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"that there is potentially going to be a number of changes .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"So I would just invite you to stay tuned","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"and in the end see","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"whether we keep the commitment","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"I made","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"to continue to honor both a woman and Alexander Hamilton and our history of democracy . ''","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"On whether the U.S. could expect multiple women on U.S. currency","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"`` What I would say is that everyone is focused on one square inch of the bill .","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"There 's two whole sides to a bill .","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"And there is a lot of space","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"to tell a lot of stories . ''","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":291,"left":162,"right":290,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":151,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":147,"right":150,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":148,"right":149,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":159,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":152,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":154,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":153,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":11,"right":156,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":156,"left":155,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":195,"right":289,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":166,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":165,"right":21,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":165,"left":17,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":163,"right":20,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":163,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"paren